            "question_hover_color": "#000000",
            "answer_color": "#6d6d6d",
            "divider_color": "#e0e0e0",
            "icon_color": "#000000",
            "question_1": "What is a Ninja Pressables Pack?",
            "answer_1": "<p>Ninja Pressables Packs are fun, themed sets of kid-friendly designs that turn clothing into a canvas for family creativity. With a mix of playful graphics in every pack, parents and kids can easily apply them to t-shirts, hoodies, or tote bags using just a household iron or heat press. It's a simple, mess-free way to bond and bring your child’s favorite designs to life.</p>",
            "question_2": "What can I apply the designs to?",
            "answer_2": "<p>You can press the designs onto <em>any</em> garment or fabric item—t-shirts, hoodies, tote bags, jackets, and more! As long as the material can handle heat, you're good to go.</p>",
            "question_3": "Do I need special equipment?",
            "answer_3": "<p>Nope! While a heat press works best, you can also use a household iron. Just follow the simple instructions included with each pack for great results.</p><p></p>",
            "question_4": "Can the transfers be washed after application?",
            "answer_4": "<p>Yes! Once applied correctly, the designs are durable, flexible, and fully washable. Your custom gear will look great wash after wash. Lab Tested for 100+ washes</p>",
            "question_5": "Are instructions included?",
            "answer_5": "<p>Yes! Every pack comes with clear, easy-to-follow instructions for both heat press and iron application. Perfect for first-timers!</p>",
            "question_6": "What age range is this best for?",
            "answer_6": "<p>These packs are ideal for kids ages 3 and up. Younger children will love picking their favorite designs, while older kids can be more hands-on in the pressing process (with help from a parent).</p>"
          },
